<noinclude>
{{Documentation|doc = 
This template is used to create a row in the infobox with social media links. It is used in the {{tll|Infobox}} template.

{{Infobox
| title = <div></div>
| 
    {{Infobox/image
    | p1 = [[File:Image.png|link=]]
    }}
    {{Infobox/socials
    | discord=https://discord.gg
    | Discord server
    }}
    {{Infobox/socials
    | steam=https://steamcommunity.com
    | Workshop page
    }}
    {{Infobox/socials
    | github=https://github.com/
    | Github repository
    }}
    {{Infobox/socials
    | bitbucket=https://bitbucket.org
    | Bitbucket repository
    }}
    {{Infobox/socials
    | X=https://x.com
    | X post
    }}
    {{Infobox/socials
    | other=https://www.google.com
    | Other link
    }}
}}

==Usage==
<pre>
{{Infobox/socials
| linkType = link
| description
}}
</pre>

===Parameters===
;{{Code|discord}}
: Link of a Discord server. This will add a Discord logo to the row.
;{{Code|steam}}
: Link of a Steam page. This will add a Steam logo to the row.
;{{Code|github}}
: Link of a Github repository. This will add a Github logo to the row.
;{{Code|bitbucket}}
: Link of a Bitbucket repository. This will add a Bitbucket logo to the row.
;{{Code|X}}
: Link of a X page. This will add a X logo to the row.
;{{Code|other}}
: Link of any other page. This will add a generic link logo to the row.
;{{Code|description}}
: The description of the link. This will be displayed next to the logo and in hypertext with the link.

}}


</noinclude><includeonly><div class="infobox-section">
<div>{{#if:{{{discord|}}}|[[File:Discord-Logo.png|link={{{discord}}}|25px]] [{{{discord}}} {{#replace:{{{1|}}}|\n|}}]|
